title: Brie and Nikki Bella are Incomparable
description:
Some would say Brie and Nikki Bella are Incomparable. Others would say that being twins who wrote a joint memoir makes them easy to compare. Either way, the two of them wrote quite honestly a compelling tale of pushing forward no matter what. This week Claire and Ashley dive into the unfamiliar world of pro wrestling and the too familiar world of reality TV with Nikki and Brie.
